1. *Pobrinut ćemo* se da svi budu zadovoljni. (We will take care that everyone is satisfied.)
2. *Pobrinula* je da svi primaju svoju nagradu. (She took care that everyone receives their reward.)
3. *Pobrinuće* se da svi budu sigurni. (They will take care that everyone is safe.)
4. *Pobrinuo* je se da ga ispratimo do vrata. (He took care that we escort him to the door.)
5. *Pobrinućemo* se da svi budu zdravi. (We will take care that everyone is healthy.)